<section id="Delete_a_Provider" remap="TID_44433">
	<title>Delete a Provider</title>
	<para>
		Request:
	</para>
	<screen>DELETE /api/provider/105</screen>
	<simpara>
		Or via the delete action as follows:
	</simpara>
	<screen>POST /api/provider/105</screen>
	<programlisting>{
  "action" : "delete"
}</programlisting>
	<para>
		Response:
	</para>
	<programlisting>{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Provider id:106 name:'rhevm102' deleting",
  "task_id": 625,
  "task_href": "http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/625",
  "href": "http://localhost:3000/api/providers/106"
}</programlisting>
	<note>
		<simpara>
			Delete actions are performed asynchronously because delete actions may take a while to complete. The delete task can be queried if needed. See <xref linkend="Querying_a_Delete_Task" />.
		</simpara>
	</note>
</section>